#: sunshine-photo-cart/includes/admin/tools/orphans.php:69
msgid ""
"It is recommended to make a backup before running this tool. Images will be "
"completely deleted from your server."
msgstr ""
"Se recomienda realizar una copia de seguridad antes de ejecutar esta "
"herramienta. Las imágenes se eliminarán por completo de su servidor."

